mkl link line advisor
file:///opt/intel/documentation_2020/en/mkl/common/mkl_link_line_advisor.htm
https://software.intel.com/en-us/articles/intel-mkl-link-line-advisor/

mkl env variable init
/opt/intel/mkl/bin$ source mklvars.sh intel64

compile
1. Set the INCLUDE, MKLROOT, LD_LIBRARY_PATH, LIBRARY_PATH, CPATH and NLSPATH environment variables in the command shell using one of mklvars script files in the 'bin' subdirectory of the Intel(R) MKL installation directory. Please see also the Intel(R) MKL User Guide.
2. gcc -o (executable) (.c)  -Wl,--start-group ${MKLROOT}/lib/intel64/libmkl_intel_lp64.a ${MKLROOT}/lib/intel64/libmkl_sequential.a ${MKLROOT}/lib/intel64/libmkl_core.a -Wl,--end-group -lpthread -lm -ldl
